div.p:
The following officers were elected: 

Mr. Sidney de la Rue, President;

Mr. Rex A. Pixley, Vice President and in charge of the fiscal
                                    administration when thus handed to the Banque;

Mr. W. H. Williams, Vice President and General Manager of the
                                    commercial side of the Banque;

Mr. Charles van Waterschoodt, Assistant Vice President,
                                    commercial side.
